{"tid":993591,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好想死，但係為咗屋企人唔敢死","createTime":"2019-01-24T04:58:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T08:12:25.000Z","uid":217683,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0e5b3b4af953aecc7c3bfbedbcee3f213a3459ad","tid":993591,"uid":217683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T04:58:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe2f24ab0cf157823a7cedaab034686bae9d3e8","tid":993591,"uid":18517,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T04:59:57.000Z","msg":"咁咪唔好死囉 咁煩既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59dbd548f2ad0a35827b75fe48c71a9d9c64944f","tid":993591,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T05:39:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc2a41e7601daeb9fa580d08d3bd93eaf294b94e","tid":993591,"uid":232605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T06:36:41.000Z","msg":"我都好想死<br />\n但諗到好多嘢好想做,又未做<br />\n就唔捨得死"},{"pid":"b1ab885689bcf904ab5601adf8ea35a77453dfdb","tid":993591,"uid":138948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T06:40:48.000Z","msg":"都好，你有目標生存落去"},{"pid":"9d190a46f4391b6d8df0be06260d06fd0ebb50c0","tid":993591,"uid":151695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T06:44:41.000Z","msg":"我都想死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過唔會走去自殺"},{"pid":"91d4d0860b2e119ea880248ce734eee0247cc611","tid":993591,"uid":155815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T06:47:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LcKpAb1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLcKpAb1.png&h=050fbbd8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9c41bf0a4ecc9a50908ee4b73c470ee9f7a088a","tid":993591,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e5b3b4af953aecc7c3bfbedbcee3f213a3459ad","tid":993591,"uid":217683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T04:58:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:04:31.000Z","msg":"相信你心中一定非常痛苦，才會如此寫下你的心聲！雖然，我並未完全了解你，但我明白置身痛苦中是怎樣一回事。有些人在困苦之中，會選擇放棄自己，不知道你是否也有這自殺的念頭？<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n無論你是否想過放棄自己，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡。因為人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=mtmXaQkNHYDFf5vLmcWqk4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=045e4b7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"b640f1322bc2f1716d028348a84bd83b9081e553","tid":993591,"uid":217683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc2a41e7601daeb9fa580d08d3bd93eaf294b94e","tid":993591,"uid":232605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T06:36:41.000Z","msg":"我都好想死<br />\n但諗到好多嘢好想做,又未做<br />\n就唔捨得死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:11:38.000Z","msg":"我之前都係 但係而家頹到咩都唔想做"},{"pid":"be6c225d9befa11df2b1254ccf2a5e2dbd6706e6","tid":993591,"uid":217683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1ab885689bcf904ab5601adf8ea35a77453dfdb","tid":993591,"uid":138948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T06:40:48.000Z","msg":"都好，你有目標生存落去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:11:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fde5a7598f8e5f42821507d1416166560458a22","tid":993591,"uid":217683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d190a46f4391b6d8df0be06260d06fd0ebb50c0"